    public class SEWeightImpl
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.impl.EObjectImpl
implements SEWeight
    An implementation of the model object 'SE Weight'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Bus P
    • Bus Q
    • Branch P
    • Branch Q
    • Bus Voltage Mag
    • Presdo
    • Zero Inj Measure
